quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Wi e hey mon he'eferɓe ɓe."
  109,2,"Mi rewata ko ndewaton ko."
  109,3,"Onon ne on ndewata ko ndewat mi ko."
  109,4,"Mi wona dewoowo ko ndewɗon ko."
  109,5,"Onon ne on ndewata ko ndewat mi ko."
  109,6,"Woodanii on diine mon inne woodanii kam diine am."
  110,1,"Si balllal Alla e udditde makka ngarii."
  110,2,"Nji'ia yimɓe heɓe naata e diine Alla he dente dente."
  110,3,"Subhina e yettudede jom ma njaafanaɗaa mo pellet ko o jaɓoowo tuubaabuya sanne."
  111,1,"Halkiima juuɗe abii lahab o halkiima."
  111,2,"Nafaani ɗum jawdi mum e ko o faggiti."
  111,3,"Ma o naat e jayngol baɗngol lewlewndu."
  111,4,"E debbo mum doondotooɗo leɗɗe o."
  111,5,"O ɗeɗɗiroyte ka daande (ɓoggol) yoora ɓadoo."